item.title: How to Schedule for Classes at MSOE
item.description: msoe-open-seat Scheduling for new classes at MSOE can be somewhat confusing and stressful. In this article, I want to quickly share a few tips and tricks I’ve learned from my time here at school. Scheduling Right around week seven or eight, you’ll receive your scheduling time in MyMSOE. Sometimes, you’ll get a late scheduling time, which means you may not be able to get all of the classes you want.
